OL,3,CAntisemitism an 'urgent issue' for all
OL,4,Cof British society, Penny Mordaunt
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FDame Penny Mordaunt has said she was
OL,8,F"stunned into silence" as she
OL,9,Fundertook a Government-backed review
OL,10,Finto antisemitism.
OL,12,FThe former Conservative minister
OL,13,Fjoined Lord John Mann, the
OL,14,FGovernment's antisemitism adviser, in
OL,15,Fchairing an independent commission on
OL,16,Fantisemitism on behalf of the Board of
OL,17,FDeputies, Britain's largest Jewish
OL,18,Fcommunity organisation.
