OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"This is an urgent issue not just for
OL,8,Fthe Jewish community but for the
OL,9,FUnited Kingdom as a whole," the pair
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FThey also said: "We are all harmed if
OL,13,Fwe tolerate the abuse of some of our
OL,14,Ffellow citizens by those who hold
OL,15,Fwarped or extreme views."
