OL,4,Cof British society, Penny Mordaunt
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FEfforts to teach primary school
OL,8,Fteachers how to avoid passing on
OL,9,Fantisemitism and anti-Jewish tropes in
OL,10,Ftheir lessons should be rolled out in
OL,11,Ffaith schools across the UK, the
OL,12,Fcommission said.
OL,14,FIt added that professional
OL,15,Forganisations and trade unions should
OL,16,Fensure that all Jewish members are
OL,17,Ftreated equally and with respect,
OL,18,Fwhile there must be a consistent
OL,19,Fapproach taken by police when dealing
OL,20,Fwith antisemitic crimes.
