OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe commission said it had seen
OL,8,Fevidence of "hidden barriers being put
OL,9,Fin front of Jewish involvement within
OL,10,Fthe arts" and said there must always
OL,11,Fbe a "robust response for those who
OL,12,Fchoose to discriminate and government
OL,13,Fat every level should ensure this".
OL,15,FLord Mann said: "It is unacceptable
OL,16,Fthat the Jewish community has faced an
OL,17,Fonslaught of antisemitism since
OL,18,FOctober 7th.
