OL,3,CAntisemitism an 'urgent issue' for all
OL,4,Cof British society, Penny Mordaunt
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"Whilst this is not new, the
OL,8,Fcommission heard shocking experiences
OL,9,Fthat we will not ignore. Antisemitism
OL,10,Fis racism and it must be treated as
OL,11,Fsuch. We hope these recommendations
OL,12,Fwill provide additional guidance and
OL,13,Faction for civil society."
OL,15,FDame Penny said: "No person should
OL,16,Fface abuse or discrimination whilst
OL,17,Fgoing about their business, whether it
OL,18,Fis pursuing the career of their choice
OL,19,For accessing public services.
