OL,4,Cof British society, Penny Mordaunt
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"We wanted to suggest some very
OL,8,Fpractical things that can be dealt
OL,9,Fwith swiftly and will dramatically
OL,10,Fimprove people's experiences."
OL,12,FBoard of Deputies president Phil
OL,13,FRosenberg said: "Overall, the
OL,14,Fchallenge in civil society can be
OL,15,Fsummarised as one of a failure to
OL,16,Fapply the protections rightly afforded
OL,17,Fto different vulnerable groups equally
OL,18,Fto Jewish people in the same positions.
